model = ComplexInnerModel({'email': {'token': 'test'}})
model.put()
result = ComplexInnerModel.fqlAll('id = %s', model._id)

model.delete()

result = ComplexInnerModel.fqlAll('id = %s', model._id)
self.assertEquals(len(result), 0)
